<s1 page = "1">
<ptxt>
Using scale (2) and gauging plastic (1), check bearing clearance with newly selected standard bearing.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If clearance still exceeds its limit, use next thicker bearing and recheck clearance, referring to 
